{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"34f452ff3a","title":"关于蒋军从大陈岛撤退时我军不要向港口一带射击的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"93e580858a","index":0,"year":1955,"month":2,"day":2,"articleId":"34f452ff3a"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji34","name":"毛泽东全集第34卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/34-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji34":{"comments":[{"id":"c5ad0f73d7","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"34f452ff3a","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这个批语写在中国人民解放军海军司令部1955年2月1日关于海岸炮兵使用的建议给中共中央军委的请示电报上。"},{"id":"e31c257b8e","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"34f452ff3a","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"彭德怀，当时任中共中央军委委员、国务院副总理兼国防部部长。"}],"contents":[{"id":"053685e945","type":"title","text":"关于蒋军从大陈岛撤退时我军不要向港口一带射击的批语！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"34f452ff3a"},{"id":"c5ad0f73d7","type":"paragraph","text":"彭德怀时同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"34f452ff3a"},{"id":"e31c257b8e","type":"paragraph","text":"在将军撤退时，无论有无美【航】均不向港口及靠近港口一带射击，即是说，让敌人安全撤走，不要贪这点小便宜。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"34f452ff3a"},{"id":"66aa076386","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"34f452ff3a"},{"id":"856062885e","type":"paragraph","text":"二月二日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"34f452ff3a"}],"page":{"id":"61ec500581","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"34f452ff3a","start":444,"end":444}}}},"__N_SSG":true}